properties.Name: Stockpile
properties.Description: A storage area or location containing a reserve or stored quantity of resource that is accrued and maintained for future use.

Columns.Name: StockpileId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a stockpile.

Columns.Name: GeographicAreaId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Geographic Area.

Columns.Name: LocationId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Location.

Columns.Name: StockpileMaximumStorageCapacityUnits
Columns.Description: The maximum storage capacity units that may be stored at the stockpile.

Columns.Name: MaximumStorageCapacityUomId
Columns.Description: The unique identifier of a Unit Of Measure.

Columns.Name: StockpileOpenedDate
Columns.Description: The date that the stockpile was opened.

Columns.Name: StockpileClosureDate
Columns.Description: The date that the stockpile was closed.

Columns.Name: StockpileNote
Columns.Description: A note, comment or additional information regarding the stockpile.
